response.overview: Mad Max becomes a pawn in a decadent oasis of a technological society, and when exiled, becomes the deliverer of a colony of children.
response.tagline: Hold out for Mad Max. This is his greatest adventure.
response.title: Mad Max Beyond Thunderdome
